reviewText: More caves is never a bad thing, I enjoy anything that can be found out about these fantastic secrets in our crust
A good dvd but a tad short at 45 mins.high quality camars used to film the exploration... Corey

Tells an interresting story, and things I knew nothing about-cave areas in Vietnam. Don't get it expecting great visuals to entertain kids-it's a cave, right? No animals, no animations, just information.
